HEADWORD: Transfeminate
<hw>Trans*fem"i*nate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>trans-</ets> + L. <ets>femina</ets> woman.]</ety> <def>To change
